cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper focuses on image-to-image translation, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model also involves semi-supervised learning, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with multi-modal and multi-domain tasks, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
